Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四戰速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 稍微靠右一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣施佩伯爵號的艦橋就看不見我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}西婭 我這就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(640,655)}Thea,jetzt zu gehen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}準備戰鬥 魚雷戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}右舷30度 目標施佩伯爵號
