Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和魚雷一同衝鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}施佩伯爵號沒有轉向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼不改變航向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小代 準備下一輪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}報告受損情況
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三號炮受損嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}二號炮中彈 還能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.14,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發動機隨時可以開足全速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.19,0:08:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是夾叉射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鈴 迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}收 收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有魚雷 已穿過施佩伯爵號艦底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.57,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然沒有迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣根本無法瞄準那個弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明瞄得那麼準
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主炮…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然我不想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣接舷奪艦的計劃根本沒辦法實行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只能重新考慮一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪 不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但只要正中一炮 這艘小船就會被打個粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.57,0:09:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不能再讓大家冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我們以前成功過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 可以試試跳艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.79,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}確實 機動性強的小型跳艇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以輕易躲開炮擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果被至近彈掀翻了的話 就只能放棄整個作戰計劃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本艦之後的指揮工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就全權交給你了 宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突擊班 準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們必須吸引施佩伯爵號的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.51,0:10:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}離預計突擊時間還有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.18,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小聰 我一打信號就開始突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}輪到咱上場了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.26,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}倒數10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向施佩伯爵號靠近200
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}4 3…準備
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真準時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繼續吸引施佩伯爵號的火力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 對方的副炮直瞄開火了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪裡被打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雷達室一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第一魚雷發射管未受創
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第二魚雷發射管一切平安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 是射擊指揮儀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}射擊指揮儀 你們還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.23,0:11:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小笠原 平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}武田 一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}日置 沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不能再讓大家冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 你一定要拿下施佩伯爵號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最大戰速 沿最短路線離開對方的射程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}離開對方射程需要多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保持最大戰速離開主炮射程需要30分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副炮則需要20分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.83,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 還要30分鐘嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第四運用類倉庫進水
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別以為你們能打倒我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知開打了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(640,655)}Wunderbar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}慢了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 進了這麼多水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟啦 百百
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她不在啊 只有我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰來幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}炮術科的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正指揮所也被毀了 閒得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}趕快修吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯 有什麼需要盡管說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把這裡堵上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家快點開到射程之外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼多水柱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 能想個辦法嗎 干擾一下對方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}船已經交給小白她們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們要為突擊班的意外情況做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}晴風號
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小白 拜託你了 保護好大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還沒好嗎 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}濕度超過90%了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}通風機是不是停了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}氣溫超過40度了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還要全速前進嗎 外面現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再堅持一下 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}宗谷同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在是我在指揮 拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 得令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們再堅持一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 這是人家的台詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}萬里小路流薙刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}被打中的話可是很痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兵因敵而制勝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.02,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}五十六
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}距離施佩伯爵號11海浬 離開她們副炮的射程了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還沒好嗎 還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}10分鐘後將離開她們的主炮射程
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這上面就是艦橋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不會放你們過去的 真知知就由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.88,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(640,655)}Mein Kapitan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(655,655)}Entschuldigung,ich bin zu spat
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.01,0:16:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 我們成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:17:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真知知 我幫上你的忙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}第十隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大功十件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美波同學 抗體都接種完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打完這針就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明乃 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小咪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}介紹一下 她就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是艦長西婭‧克萊采 事情我都聽她說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝你救了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是晴風號艦長岬明乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}副艦長 宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你們所有人都沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們準備回希亞德勒基地補給
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小咪也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 當然會和我們一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保險起見回去以後接受一下精密體檢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飯做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是三文魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(655,655)}Lachsfilet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還可以叫做壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也有幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還放了馬鈴薯球和鯡魚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}壽司 生魚片 還有過勞死？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.92,0:18:28.15,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}※正確的叫法很可能是Kluski。\N\h\h\h\h又及，過勞死這個單字的日文讀法及其意義被直接挪用到了英語圈及德語圈。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後那個說錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是大鍋菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.44,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 艦長 還可以叫關東煮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}關東煮？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 說句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}經過我們不斷地努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.67,0:18:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}終於光復了艦船 恢復了意識
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這個值得慶祝的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有請晴風號的艦長帶頭乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.41,0:18:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.03,0:19:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那麼 各位 乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Prost
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來 艦長 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是香腸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是我們船上特製的香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就想吃這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}味道真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長 老夫一直代你保管著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幫我戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}艦長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.00,0:20:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過你們的船好像受損很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這都是拜誰所賜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過 技術還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然離打敗我們還差那麼一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要不要和我們一起回希亞德勒維修
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不了 我們接到命令準備和明石號會合
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎 那就要在此道別了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}酒杯我這就還你 以後別把我當晴風號的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要我回 我也不回了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟你們在一起很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我們也是 一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(640,655)}Gute reise
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老夫要上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這筆生意還是虧本了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:22:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在已經身無分文了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:06.99,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352.333,500)}多災多難的明娜作戰！
Comment: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:07.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,ED-FF
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:13.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:19.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}言葉よりも優しく　背中を押すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:25.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}そう　私と君のripple effect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:42.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}果てなく向かってくる波は険しいばかりで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:49.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}航路はどうしよう　君と選ぶ未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:55.54,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}微笑み忘れたら　私が笑うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:23:03.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}涙弾けたあとは　強さが水面に広がるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:12.32,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}七つの青は今日も　世界を包んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:16.61,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}言葉よりも優しく波打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:20.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}晴れた空とあの風と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:26.78,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}誰かのそばで　夢を描くのならば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:30.42,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}その誰かが私でありたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:35.35,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}きっと春が待ってくれてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:13.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.78,0:22:19.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}我會比話語還要溫柔 輕輕地推著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:25.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}是啊 這就是你和我之間的漣漪效應
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:42.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}面前的驚濤駭浪 一浪捲來一浪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.70,0:22:49.04,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HD2B857&}我們選擇的航路 就是我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.52,0:22:55.54,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}如果你忘記了微笑 我會笑給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:23:03.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&H6777D1&}流過眼淚之後 讓堅強隨波布散
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.49,0:23:12.32,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}青色七洋 今天也環繞著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:16.61,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}比話語還要溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:20.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HE5C040&}是這片晴空和習習涼風
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.43,0:23:26.78,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}如果你希望有人能陪你一起描繪夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:30.42,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}我希望我就是那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:35.35,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\3c&HCAA83F&}要相信春天正在等待著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.29,0:23:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事情還算順利 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是晴風號卻受損得這麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:24:00.09,End,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472.667,587.333)}下集老夫也要看片！
